" F2 行号开关，用于鼠标复制代码用
" 为方便复制，用<F2>开启/关闭行号显示:
function! HideNumber()
    if(&relativenumber == &number)
        set relativenumber! number!
    elseif(&number)
        set number!
    else
        set relativenumber!
    endif
    set number?
endfunc
" ,m 显示/隐藏行号
nnoremap <leader>m :call HideNumber()<CR>
" ,l 换行开关
nnoremap <leader>' :set wrap! wrap?<CR>
" ,, 语法开关，关闭语法可以加快大文件的展示
nnoremap <leader>, :exec exists('syntax_on') ? 'syn off' : 'syn on'<CR>


